the ghost I was tracking.

273
00:31:09.838 --> 00:31:12.640
But I didn't know your name.
Just your face. your habits.

274
00:31:12.774 --> 00:31:15.577
And once I was able
to establish a pattern.

275
00:31:15.710 --> 00:31:18.212
